      "1226198493522527": {
        "description": "Intended for the Twitch Bloxfest event. Will be removed soon after the event.\n\nEscape Hotel & Mines.\n\nREAD CAREFULLY:\n\n- NO MODIFIERS\n- NO REVIVES. Your teammates can revive themselves, but they won't get the badge.\n- NO REVIVING THROUGH CONTINUE RUN.\n- NO USE OF LOTUS\n- NO USE OF SAVES. This might be inconvenient for non-competitors, but we needed to make sure nobody could cheat by using old saves.\n- NOBODY IN THE RUN CAN USE ANY RIFT WHATSOEVER.\n\n- You CAN use detours through the Outdoors; escaping the Hotel through the room 90 detour counts, and entering from the Outdoors halfway into the Mines counts.\n- You CAN purchase items in the Pre-Run shop.\n- You CAN run this multiplayer or singleplayer.\n- You CAN do this in one marathon run starting from the Hotel, and it is the most time efficient method, especially if you use the Outdoors detour.\n- You CAN do this in separate runs. ",
        "enabled": true,
        "icon_image_id": 96828844400548,
        "id": "1226198493522527",
        "name": "BLOXFEST: Double Feature",
        "updated": "2026-02-18T00:35:38.07+00:00"
      },
